subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Lukas Rosol, ranked 100th, pulled off one of the biggest upsets of the past decade in men’s tennis, blasting his way past Rafael Nadal in the second round at Wimbledon.
